summary: WILMINGTON, Mass., January 21, 2026--Charles River Laboratories Schedules Fourth-Quarter 2025 Earnings and 2026 Guidance Release and Conference Call

headline: Charles River Enters Manufacturing Collaboration with Gazi University
summary: WILMINGTON, Mass., January 21, 2026--Charles River Laboratories International, Inc. (NYSE: CRL) and Gazi University Faculty of Medicine, today announced a gene therapy contract development and manufacturing organization (CDMO) collaboration, providing plasmid DNA for AAV production and in vitro efficacy studies.
